        <updateDate>2005-10-28T19:57:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Repeal of Federal Reserve Board Term Limitation Act - Amends the Federal Reserve Act to repeal the term limitation on Federal Reserve Board membership.</p> <p>Provides that any member of the Board who has served a full term of 14 years is eligible for reappointment to a five-year term.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
